<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.8.5">
<l>ciṉamēvu maṭalariyi ṉuruva mākit tiṟalmēvu miraṇiyaṉa tākaṅ kīṇṭu</l>
<l>maṉamēvu vañcaṉaiyāl vanta pēycci māḷavuyir vavviyavem māyōṉ kāṇmiṉ</l>
<l>iṉamēvu varivaḷaikkai yēntuṅ kōvai yēyvāya marakatampōl kiḷiyi ṉiṉcol</l>
<l>aṉamēvu naṭaimaṭavār payiluñ celvat taṇiyaḻuntūr niṉṟukanta vamarar kōvē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Our Māyōṉ who, having become an anger-filled, murderous lion in form,</l>
<l rend="indent">splitting Hiraṇya’s hatred-filled chest,</l>
<l>Snatched the life so the demoness, who came with deceit</l>
<l rend="indent">that filled [her] mind, perished,</l>
<l>Behold, is the king of immortals who is happy</l>
<l rend="indent">standing in lovely, prosperous Aḻuntūr,</l>
<l rend="indent">where dwell simple maids with gaits that swans desire,</l>
<l>Lips like [rosy] kōvai [fruit], the sweet speech of an emerald-like parrot,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] who bear on their arms striped bangles joined in bunches.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
